description:
MindCrack is a server Guude started in late 2010. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

Today we go ABBA Rules caving with the crazy viking man, AnderZEL.
http://www.youtube.com/user/ImAnderZEL

In ABBA Rules caving, players race and compete with each other to collect the most ores within a chosen time limit. The ores are worth various points. Whoever gets the most points wins and gets to keep everything.

(Ore Points)
Emerald = 7
Diamond = 5
Gold = 3
Redstone = 1
Lapis = 1
